snippet.title: Pokémon Masters EX | 5.5 Year Celebration 🎉
snippet.description:
Celebrate 5.5 years of Pokémon Masters EX’s 5.5 with new Master Sync Pairs featuring May (Champion) & Shiny Primal Kyogre and Brendon (Champion) & Shiny Primal Groudon!

🌊 May (Champion) & Shiny Primal Kyogre are available from Friday, February 28 at 6:00 UTC through Wednesday, April 9 at 5:59 UTC. 

⛰️ Brendon (Champion) & Shiny Primal Groudon are available from Sunday, March 2 at 6:00 UTC through Wednesday, April 9 at 5:59 UTC.

Download Pokémon Masters EX today and join the fun! 

Official site: https://www.pokemon.com
